Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很重要的东西啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随意弄丢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,武一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也能把爱找出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的只有渡你一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定会找到爱给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你便去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能得到松明之火了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你自己相信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要干多余的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十六话\N展望光辉的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到世界的终结去找爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,这样一口气掷出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡真水皮,你自己去拾回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已回去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,快坐上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的货车了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不上去的话便再逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不回家的话,妈妈会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,已没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的妈妈一定已乘上别的货车了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在人类想像不到的世界末日已迫近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所有的机场,所有的港口,还有所有的主要公路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都充满了避难的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,在这个地球上还有安全的地方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地球只有被消灭的命运吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳吞噬地球的时限已一分一秒的迫近…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳吞噬地球?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳吞噬地球是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么也不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳突然的膨胀起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,到昨天为止还不是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被隐藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳变大了会怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事也不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当那太阳西沈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再次升起的时候便是末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已不能再看见太阳升起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的,妈妈会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友,你去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈一定是在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住的镇有这样的地方吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到刚才为止还是那么热的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清晨吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个海是清晨的海洋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说是黄昏?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看像哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔,你为什么不逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为画这幅画是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我想已没有人会来看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳会吞噬地球是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一点也不热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又说太阳不会再升起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升起的时候便是世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,会升起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们不放弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳一定会升起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深信着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幅画什么时候会完成?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,为什么要画海洋?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我们的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是由海洋孕育出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由海洋?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋是生命的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是从海洋和太阳的力量中得到生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个太阳为何要把人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有生物消灭呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为人类变得太聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此便开始发怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发怒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类开始觉得自己是世上最了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且什么也做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类砍下一棵树会夺去多少生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事想也没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些草、树木和昆虫们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会都是因为人类而死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好的不是人类吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是应该更早发现这些事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那数不尽的星星内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有由今天开始诞生的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有今日死去的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是回到了宇宙的自然之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这宇宙中…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有和我们同一命运的星星吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后,今后也会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些星星会知道我们的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不会再犯同样的错误了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像曾经和叔叔在哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里见过呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝对不会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天太阳也一定会升起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不只是靠你一个人的力量生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这无边的宇宙中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予了你生存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予了你面对所有困难的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用全身去感受那力量并且相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有那力量存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是绝对不会灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的太阳也一定会升起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深信着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔!
