Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是你得到的新力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个才是龙星丸真正的样子
