Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信你自己的力量战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
