Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了呢,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好啊!
